    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You spend an hour muttering incantations while finely etching a rune into a surface. Once it is ready, you hold a handful of diamond dust, imbuing it with power, before pushing it into the surface of the rune where it is absorbed. Magically hidden, your rune lies ready to unleash its power at a chosen trigger.</em></p><p><strong>Materials</strong> : You require 0.2 pounds of pure @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wV3r0XKYOLYdI0nz]{Diamond Dust}, typically valued at 100 gold. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><strong>Create Runes</strong> </p><ul><li><p>Choose a 5 ft. space in which to create the @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-summoned-creatures.Actor.HXJxb6KheaCkjNFz]{rune}. If the rune is somehow moved 5 ft. or more, the spell ends. You set a condition for the rune to detonate (such as the rune's text being read aloud, or at least two undead being in the blast radius). You can also detonate the rune at any time using your reaction.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong> </p><p>The explosion has a 20 ft. radius.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 5d8]] damage*. Damage can be &amp;reference[acid], &amp;reference[cold], &amp;reference[fire], &amp;reference[thunder], or &amp;reference[lightning] damage (your choice).</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d8]] for each spell level above 3rd.</p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Materials</strong> : You require 0.2 pounds of pure @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wV3r0XKYOLYdI0nz]{Diamond Dust}, typically valued at 100 gold. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><strong>Create Runes</strong> </p><ul><li><p>Choose a 5 ft. space in which to create the @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-summoned-creatures.Actor.HXJxb6KheaCkjNFz]{rune}. If the rune is somehow moved 5 ft. or more, the spell ends. You set a condition for the rune to detonate (such as the rune's text being read aloud, or at least two undead being in the blast radius). You can also detonate the rune at any time using your reaction.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong> </p><p>The explosion has a 20 ft. radius.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 5d8]] damage*. Damage can be &amp;reference[acid], &amp;reference[cold], &amp;reference[fire], &amp;reference[thunder], or &amp;reference[lightning] damage (your choice).</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d8]] for each spell level above 3rd.</p>"
